      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained by its previous owner. The exterior retains a strong shine, though you may find a few minor stone chips and light surface scratches upon close inspection. Inside, the cabin is clean and free of major wear, with all electronics and climate controls functioning as they should. Mechanically, the car runs smoothly and has a consistent service history, making it a reliable choice for anyone looking for a dependable vehicle that still looks great on the road.",
