      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with this absolute stunner. Honestly, it\u2019s in incredible shape\u2014it looks and drives just like it did the day it rolled off the lot! I've totally babied this car, so you're getting a real gem that's ready for its next adventure. It's basically flawless and waiting for a new home. Come take a look, you're going to love it!",
      "price": 44500.0,
