    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a superlative 2002 BMW M3 (E46) in collector-grade condition. This chassis is powered by the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure double-VANOS system for precise valve timing across the 8,000 RPM powerband. Mechanically, this unit is beyond reproach: the rod bearings have been replaced with treated shells, and the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced with structural plates to prevent floor failure. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock. The suspension retains its factory kinematics with refreshed bushings and dampers, ensuring the original turn-in characteristics remain sharp. The exterior finish and interior Nappa leather show no signs of UV degradation or mechanical wear. This is a turn-key example for the purist who demands peak atmospheric performance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
