    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional 2021 Audi S5 Sportback in Mythos Black Metallic over Magma Red Fine Nappa leather. This vehicle has been maintained to a standard rarely seen, kept in a climate-controlled garage and hand-washed exclusively using the two-bucket method. The exterior paint is flawless, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating that produces a deep, mirror-like finish; there are zero stone chips, swirl marks, or scratches. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition\u2014the leather bolsters show no signs of entry wear, and the original factory fragrance still lingers. Mechanically, it is perfect, with a full service history documented through a single authorized Audi dealership and all preventative maintenance performed ahead of schedule. The 19-inch Cavo-design wheels are pristine with no curb rash, wrapped in fresh Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to acquire a vehicle that is indistinguishable from new, offered with both keys, all original manuals, and a clean title in hand.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
